# Cross-Repo Rule Read Requirement

- At the start of each new session, read all `.mdc` rule files in:
  - `C:/Source/RentAll/RentAll.Api/.cursor/rules`
  - `C:/Source/RentAll/RentAll.Ui/.cursor/rules`
  - `C:/Source/RentAll/RentAll.Db/.cursor/rules`
- If a repo or rules folder is missing, explicitly state that it was checked and no rules were found there.
- After reading, verbally list every rule file path read.
- End that startup acknowledgment with: `Ready to go.`
